01:06:49,310 --> 01:06:50,350
Sayang.

1058
01:06:50,410 --> 01:06:53,450
Pekerjaanmu bermasalah?

1059
01:06:54,180 --> 01:06:56,520
Kudengar Cha Hee Kyung

